Write tests
Code coverage of tests
Write larger example program
Implement the missing functionality (see below).


The following "core" functionality is currently not supported by
   HOpenCL:

  clCreateContextFromType
  clCreateSubBuffer
  clEnqueueReadBufferRect
  clEnqueueWriteBufferRect
  clEnqueueCopyBufferRect
  clEnqueueUnmapMemObject
  clCreateProgramWithBinary
  clUnloadCompiler
  clEnqueueNativeKernel

Events and synchronization:
  clCreateContext: Support adding callback error function
  clSetUserEventStatus
  clWaitForEvents
  clSetEventCallback

  clEnqueueMarker
  clEnqueueBarrier
  clEnqueueWaitForEvents
  clFlush
  clFinish


The following full sections of the OpenCL standard is not supported:
---------------------------------------------------------------------
 * Image Objects
 * Sampler Objects
 * Profiling of memory objects and kernels
 * Extensions of the OpenCL standard
 * OpenGL and D3D related functions

